  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/986ca8bccb0bbbf78dd69965a3d9da41.poster.avif?t=1770106138\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/986ca8bccb0bbbf78dd69965a3d9da41.webm?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/986ca8bccb0bbbf78dd69965a3d9da41.mp4?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend Lumi, a lost girl who lives on your desktop. Work together to recover her memories of who she is and why she appeared on your computer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/a8cc25d1dbc56d1a4aa9351580cb54fe.poster.avif?t=1770106138\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/a8cc25d1dbc56d1a4aa9351580cb54fe.webm?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/a8cc25d1dbc56d1a4aa9351580cb54fe.mp4?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your own computer to solve desktop puzzles and unlock memory files.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ef60098072e49a18a39d8001c759f614.poster.avif?t=1770106138\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ef60098072e49a18a39d8001c759f614.webm?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ef60098072e49a18a39d8001c759f614.mp4?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a story with the worst characters ever written.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ad7f42b1da8a64d696471754ba046568.poster.avif?t=1770106138\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ad7f42b1da8a64d696471754ba046568.webm?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/ad7f42b1da8a64d696471754ba046568.mp4?t=1770106138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the worst characters ever written. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1275670/extras/6ca9a554ec18bfc7d935ea436491a8ec.avif?t=1770106138\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sure, every game on Steam has a wishlist button. But is it as good as Outcore's wishlist button? Scientists have proved that clicking this wishlist button an uneven number of times can increase your lifespan.</p>",
